    "Many studies (Gardner 1985; Oroujlou & Vahedi, 2011; Getie 2020) have noted an important connection between language positivity and culture.",
    "The language instructors must promote integrative motivation among ESL/EFL learners.",
    "This study investigated Saudi EFL learners' attitudes towards studying English as a foreign language, their motivation, and the contextual and surrounding elements that impacting their opinions positively or negatively.",
    "It was found that Saudi EFL learners had highly positive attitudes towards learning English language.",
    "It was also revealed that they had a higher degree of instrumental motivation but a lower degree of integrative motivation."
  ],
